Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
com.example.javafx_clinicmanager.Appointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Imaging
public class Appointment extends Object implements Comparable<Appointment>
The Appointment class models an appointment in a scheduling system. It implements the Comparable interface, allowing appointments to be compared and sorted based on defined criteria
Author:
Deep Patel, Manan Patel
